      "repair_reason": "structured ClawSweeper needs-human verdict with repairable P-severity findings (sha=8209b7039b0a11127417fc4bd466ed4a679bb9bb)",
      "review_summary": "The PR imports `matchesNoProxy` into `src/agents/tools/web-guarded-fetch.ts` and switches NO_PROXY-matched `web_fetch` requests from trusted-env-proxy mode to strict guarded fetch mode.\n\nPR surface: Source +4. Total +4 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the patch defect from source: current main already skips EnvHttpProxyAgent when `NO_PROXY` matches, then uses the strict pinned SSRF path. I did not run a live proxy/web_fetch reproduction in this read-only review.",
      "review_followup": "- [P1] Manual maintainer/security review is needed because this PR is one of several competing candidates and the remaining decision is whether NO_PROXY should imply direct local/private web_fetch access.",
      "freeform_prompt": null,
